                <head>48. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d48fn1">Source: National Security Council,
                        Carter Administration Intelligence Files, Box I022, <gloss
                            corresp="#t_SCCI_1">SCC–I</gloss> on Covert Action, 6 August 1980.
